uote><blockquote>頭頂飛起果啲頭髮可以用搽呢種膏禁返低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/204650_1e1833032664093f0f04874e1224942d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F204650_1e1833032664093f0f04874e1224942d.jpg&h=08618637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬寧/759/卓悅有<br />\n以前聽過人講萬寧$60左右<br />\n之後我係卓悅買$38定$39<br />\n綠色係for比較硬既髮質，我諗鳩毛頭都係買綠色好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於鳩毛本身就做負離子吧啦，我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係頭頂果d似鳩毛 其他正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾<br />\n用完個頭好立但又平復唔到,太重手又會好似有層蠟咁<br />\n可能係因為我啲髮質差到佢都幫唔到我"},{"pid":"1ad3837a06dbb73215775adff2aaafffb9701db3","tid":196473,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba01cbd5fc418b3801aa55eac14bb82de9c2fcd6","tid":196473,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b82da669c2d4a658eed69f90b6bbead9ddb55c7","tid":196473,"uid":79281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d42cc051c820fe5a287d71d07cb1e7aa1a748c","tid":196473,"uid":8986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"頭髮乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗完頭再吹頭 <br />\nD頭髮乾到可以吉到手指"},{"pid":"2c28ae788bcafcfef401057d9a2eea9557941fcf","tid":196473,"uid":76727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:52:13.000Z","msg":"嗚啊<br />\n終於有同路人喇<br />\n本身已經係天生攣毛 但我上半個頭既頭髮髮質基本上同鳩毛差唔多 又硬又粗又攣 就咁睇落我d頭髮係上曲下直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲係成條仲攣過公仔麵咁波浪型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經有一排發顛係咁炆曬啲攣毛 以後一天光曬 但個排最後變禿頭嚇撚死我<br />\n但唔知好彩定唔好彩 之後生翻曬啲頭髮出黎 但新生個啲全部都係鳩毛咁既頭髮 個排個頭上半part就係一舊野咁 好崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然而加已經長翻 但都係好明顯好多毛毛飛曬出黎 啲頭髮一樣咁硬 又罕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪真係只可以keep住去焗油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 藍絲<br />\n真心想請教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}